早在2014年8月，[[巴西东北部|巴西东北部]]城市[[纳塔尔_(巴西)|纳塔尔]]的医护人员便开始调查一种病症为出现粉红色扁平皮疹、眼充血、发烧、关节疼痛和头痛的疾病疫情。尽管病症类似于登革热，但测试排除了登革热和其他几个潜在病因。到2015年3月，疾病传播到[[巴伊亚州|巴伊亚州]][[萨尔瓦多_(巴西)|萨尔瓦多]]，至此病情已在三个州份出现<ref name=McNeil6Feb>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/07/health/zika-virus-brazil-how-it-spread-explained.html |title=How a Medical Mystery in Brazil Led Doctors to Zika |work=The New York Times |date=2016-02-06 |accessdate=2016-03-06 |first1=Donald G. |last1=McNeil, Jr. |first2=Simon |last2=Romero |first3=Sabrina |last3=Tavernise |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182837/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/07/health/zika-virus-brazil-how-it-spread-explained.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随后，2015年5月，[[巴伊亚联邦大学|巴伊亚联邦大学]]和{{le|伊万德罗·查加斯研究所|Evandro Chagas Institute}}的研究人员利用[[逆转录聚合酶链式反应|逆转录聚合酶链式反应]]测试，断定疾病其实是寨卡病毒疫情<ref name="Identificado vírus causador">{{cite news |url=http://g1.globo.com/bahia/noticia/2015/04/identificado-virus-causador-de-doenca-misteriosa-em-salvador-e-rms.html |title=Identificado vírus causador de doença misteriosa em Salvador e RMS – notícias em Bahia |date=2015-04-29 |work={{tsl|en|GloboNews||GloboNews}} |location=São Paulo |language=pt |accessdate=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518101940/http://g1.globo.com/bahia/noticia/2015/04/identificado-virus-causador-de-doenca-misteriosa-em-salvador-e-rms.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Zika virus – Brazil: confirmed">{{cite web |url=http://www.promedmail.org/direct.php?id=3370768 |title=Zika virus – Brazil: confirmed |publisher=International Society for Infectious Diseases |website=ProMED-mail |date=2015-05-19 |accessdate=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2016-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130023132/http://www.promedmail.org/direct.php?id=3370768 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[寨卡病毒|寨卡病毒]]于1947年在栖息于[[乌干达|乌干达]][[恩德培|恩德培]]附近森林的[[普通猕猴|普通猕猴]]身上发现<ref name="DuffyChen2009">{{cite journal | first1=Mark R. | url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa0805715 | title=Zika virus outbreak on Yap Islands, Federated States of Micronesia | date=2009-06-11 | last2=Chen | first2=Tai-Ho | last3=Hancock | first3=W. Thane | journal=[[新英格兰医学杂志|The New England Journal of Medicine]] | issue=24 | last1=Duffy | volume=360 | pages=2536–2543 | doi=10.1056/NEJMoa0805715 | pmid=19516034 | access-date=2017-05-28 | archive-date=2015-10-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025200058/http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa0805715 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。尽管血清证据表明随后几十年来在非洲和亚洲部分地区陆续有人感染病毒<ref name="Zika virus outside Africa">{{cite journal |url=http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/eid/article/15/9/09-0442 |title=Zika virus outside Africa |publisher=[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] |date=September 2009 |last=Hayes |first=Edward B. |journal={{tsl|en|Emerging Infectious Diseases||Emerging Infectious Diseases}} |volume=15 |issue=9 |pages=1347–1350 |issn=1080-6059 |doi=10.3201/eid1509.090442 |pmc=2819875 |pmid=19788800}}</ref>，但在{{le|2007年雅浦岛寨卡病毒疫情|2007 Yap Islands Zika virus outbreak}}之前，仅有14宗人类感染寨卡病毒病例记录在案<ref name="DuffyChen2009" />。

研究人员渐渐相信一位在[[法属波利尼西亚|法属波利尼西亚]]被蚊子叮咬而受感染的旅客将病毒带回巴西，从而感染其他人<ref name="Romero29Jan">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/30/world/americas/tears-and-bewilderment-in-brazilian-city-facing-zika-crisis.html |title=Tears and Bewilderment in Brazilian City Facing Zika Crisis |work=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]] |date=2016-01-29 |accessdate=2016-02-01 |first=Simon |last=Romero |archive-date=2016-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131100752/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/30/world/americas/tears-and-bewilderment-in-brazilian-city-facing-zika-crisis.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Zika Virus Transmission from French Polynesia to Brazil">{{cite journal |accessdate=2016-03-08 |first1=Didier |last1=Musso |url=http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/eid/article/21/10/15-1125_article |title=Zika Virus Transmission from French Polynesia to Brazil |publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention |date=October 2015 |journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases |volume=21 |issue=10 |page=1887 |doi=10.3201/eid2110.151125 |archive-date=2016-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320003447/http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/eid/article/21/10/15-1125_article |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Murthy28Jan">{{cite news |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Health/zika-virus-outbreak-brazil-linked-major-sporting-events/story?id=36575321 |title=Origin of Zika Virus Outbreak in Brazil May Be Linked to Major Sporting Events |work=[[ABC新聞|ABC News]] |date=2016-01-28 |accessdate=2016-03-06 |last=Murthy |first=Bhavini |archive-date=2016-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302040943/http://abcnews.go.com/Health/zika-virus-outbreak-brazil-linked-major-sporting-events/story?id=36575321 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[系统发生学|系统发生学家]]分析了巴西首宗感染病例，明显发现循环病毒是亚洲病毒株，而非非洲，且与法属波利尼西亚疫情的病毒基因相似<ref name="Zika Virus Transmission from French Polynesia to Brazil"/><ref name="Murthy28Jan"/>。寨卡病毒从非洲和亚洲传到大洋洲再到美洲的路线，可能反映出目前在美洲相当大一部分地区流行的基孔肯雅热病和登革热的传播路线<ref name="Zika virus: following the path of dengue and chikungunya?">{{cite journal |date=2015-07-18 |first1=D |journal=The Lancet |last1=Musso |title=Zika virus: following the path of dengue and chikungunya? |last2=Cao-Lormeau |first2=VM |last3=Gubler |first3=DJ |url=http://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(15)61273-9/fulltext |volume=386 |issue=9990 |pages=243–4 |pmid=26194519 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(15)61273-9 |access-date=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616033544/https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(15)61273-9/fulltext |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

直到2016年3月，病毒穿入巴西的特殊事件才明朗。巴西研究人员认为，寨卡病毒在[[2014年世界杯足球赛|2014年世界杯足球赛]]期间登陆的<ref name="Romero29Jan"/>。而法国研究人员推测则病毒是在不久后的2014年8月登陆的，当时到[[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]参加世界皮划艇短距离锦标赛的队员，来自{{le|2013-2014年大洋洲寨卡病毒疫情|2013–2014 Zika virus outbreaks in Oceania|已经或正在经历寨卡病毒疫情}}的法属波利尼西亚、[[新喀里多尼亚|新喀里多尼亚]]、[[复活节岛|复活节岛]]和[[库克群岛|库克群岛]]<ref name="McNeil6Feb"/><ref name="Zika Virus Transmission from French Polynesia to Brazil"/>。然而，法属波利尼西亚的疫情到2014年2月达到顶峰并急剧下降，不禁令人怀疑病毒是在当年晚些时候由观众和参赛选手来到巴西的推测<ref name=McNeil24Mar/>。2016年3月，《[[科学_(期刊)|科学]]》杂志发表了一篇基于样本相对较小的病毒突变数目的“{{le|分子时钟|Molecular clock}}”研究报告，认为寨卡病毒是在2013年5月到12月间从法属波利尼西亚登陆美洲（最有可能在巴西），恰好在世界杯和皮划艇锦标赛之前<ref name=McNeil24Mar>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/25/health/one-traveler-may-have-brought-zika-to-the-americas-in-2013.html|title=One Traveler May Have Brought Zika to the Americas in 2013|work=The New York Times|date=2016-03-24|accessdate=2016-03-24|first=Donald G., Jr.|last=McNeil|archive-date=2016-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324185902/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/25/health/one-traveler-may-have-brought-zika-to-the-americas-in-2013.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。文章提到，伐利亚（{{lang|en|Faria}}）和同事们设法追踪在巴西循环的病毒株源头，发现相比法属波利尼西亚的菌株，该菌株遗传变异性极小。在将从法属波利尼西亚抵达巴西的游客数目和当年报告病例数和举办的活动联系起来后，团队推断病毒于[[2013年国际足联联合会杯|2013年国际足联联合会杯]]期间来到巴西，当时塔西提岛队和其他球队在巴西数个城市比赛，吸引众多两国游客观赛<ref name="FariaAzevedo2016">{{cite journal | date=2016-03-24 | display-authors=3 | first1=N. R. | first10=I. | first11=I. M. | first12=J. S. | first13=A. Y. | first14=F. G. d. S. | first15=F. L. d. L. | first16=A. | first17=S. G. | first18=A. C. R. | first19=B. T. | url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2016/03/23/science.aaf5036 | first2=R. d. S. d. S. | first20=D. B. d. A. | first21=D. S. G. | first22=A. L. | first23=E. V. P. d. | first24=D. F. | first25=E. S. | first26=C. S. | first27=L. C. | first28=H. B. | first29=L. M. N. | first3=M. U. G. | first30=D. d. B. | first31=J. P. | first32=L. | first33=J. | first34=L. C. J. | first35=M. M. d. | first36=M. | first37=S. I. | first38=R. S. | first39=P. d. S. | first4=R. | first40=L. F. d. | first41=C. P. S. | first42=S. P. | first43=J. M. d. | first44=L. | first45=J. F. | first46=J. L. d. S. G. | first47=D. | first48=G. | first49=E. | first5=M. S. | first50=K. | first51=M. | first52=G. E. | first53=W. K. | first54=R. | first55=O. G. | first56=M. R. T. | first57=P. F. C. | last1=Faria | last10=Rissanen | last11=Rocco | last12=Nogueira | last13=Maeda | last14=Vasami | last15=Macedo | last16=Suzuki | last17=Rodrigues | last18=Cruz | last19=Nunes | last2=Azevedo | last20=Medeiros | last21=Rodrigues | last22=Nunes Queiroz | last23=Silva | last24=Henriques | last25=Travassos da Rosa | last26=de Oliveira | last27=Martins | last28=Vasconcelos | last29=Casseb | last3=Kraemer | last30=Simith | last31=Messina | last32=Abade | last33=Lourenco | last34=Alcantara | last35=Lima | last36=Giovanetti | last37=Hay | last38=de Oliveira | last39=Lemos | last4=Souza | last40=Oliveira | last41=de Lima | last42=da Silva | last43=Vasconcelos | last44=Franco | last45=Cardoso | last46=Vianez-Junior | last47=Mir | last48=Bello | last49=Delatorre | last5=Cunha | last50=Khan | last51=Creatore | last52=Coelho | last53=de Oliveira | last54=Tesh | last55=Pybus | last56=Nunes | last57=Vasconcelos | title=Zika virus in the Americas: Early epidemiological and genetic findings | last6=Hill | first6=S. C. | last7=Theze | first7=J. | last8=Bonsall | first8=M. B. | last9=Bowden | first9=T. A. | journal=Science | volume=352 | issue=6283 | pages=345–9 | issn=0036-8075 | doi=10.1126/science.aaf5036 | pmid=27013429 | pmc=4918795 | bibcode=2016Sci...352..345F | access-date=2017-05-28 | archive-date=2016-04-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405215403/http://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2016/03/23/science.aaf5036 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。寨卡病毒的症状一般非常轻微或没有，因此巴西用了近一年的时间从确诊首个病例。但到那时，疫情已经很普遍。病毒在巴西迅速蔓延的因素还包括非免疫人口、人口密度高、热带气候和该国防控埃及斑蚊的力度不足<ref name="AiZhang2016">{{cite journal |first1=Jing-Wen |last1=Ai |script-title=en:Zika virus outbreak: ‘a perfect storm’ |last2=Zhang |first2=Ying |last3=Zhang |first3=Wenhong |journal=Emerging Microbes and Infections |publisher=Shanghai Shangyixun Cultural Communication |url=http://www.nature.com/emi/journal/v5/n3/full/emi201642a.html |date=2016-02-23 |volume=5 |issue=3 |page=e21 |issn=2222-1751 |doi=10.1038/emi.2016.42 |access-date=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2016-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130042532/http://www.nature.com/emi/journal/v5/n3/full/emi201642a.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自2015年初，美洲和加勒比海40国<ref name="PAHOGeographicDistribution">{{cite web | url=http://ais.paho.org/phip/viz/ed_zika_countrymap.asp | title=Geographic distribution of confirmed autochthonous cases of Zika virus (vector-borne transmission) in countries and territories of the Americas, 2015-2016 | publisher=[[泛美卫生局|Pan American Health Organization]] | work=Epidemic Diseases–Zika in the Americas | date=2016-05-26 | accessdate=2016-05-30 | archive-date=2016-06-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160614150002/http://ais.paho.org/phip/viz/ed_zika_countrymap.asp | dead-url=no }}</ref>、西太平洋16国和非洲1国报告了确诊病例（[[#ZikaCases|见表]]）。许多国家报告的蚊子传播病例并没有报告为寨卡病例，病人出现病症之前，移居自或从受寨卡影响地区归来（[[#ZikaCases|见表]]）。

== 传播 ==
{{See also|寨卡病毒#传播方式}}
[[File:Aedes_aegypti.jpg|thumb]]是携带寨卡病毒的[[载体_(生物学)|载体]]。]]
寨卡是[[蚊子传播的疾病|蚊子传播的疾病]]，也可以由男性[[性傳染病|性传播]]给他的性伴侣<ref name="CDC Sexual Transmission Guideline 1 Apr">{{cite journal | first1=Alexandra M. | last1=Oster | url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/volumes/65/wr/mm6512e3.htm | title=Update: Interim Guidance for Prevention of Sexual Transmission of Zika Virus — United States, 2016 | date=2016-04-01 | display-authors=3 | last2=Russell | first2=Kate | last3=Stryker | first3=Jo Ellen | last4=Friedman | first4=Allison | last5=Kachur | first5=Rachel E. | last6=Petersen | first6=Emily E. | last7=Jamieson | first7=Denise J. | last8=Cohn | first8=Amanda C. | last9=Brooks | first9=John T. | journal=MMWR. Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report | volume=65 | issue=12 | pages=323–325 | doi=10.15585/mmwr.mm6512e3 | pmid=27032078 | access-date=2017-05-28 | archive-date=2020-10-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030025624/https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/volumes/65/wr/mm6512e3.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。过去二三十年，[[埃及伊蚊|埃及伊蚊]]在全球范围内的复苏，使得它成为分布最广的蚊子之一<ref name="ECDC Aedes aegypti">{{cite web |url=http://ecdc.europa.eu/en/healthtopics/vectors/mosquitoes/Pages/aedes-aegypti.aspx |title=Aedes aegypti |publisher=European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control |accessdate=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2017-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710145706/https://ecdc.europa.eu/en/healthtopics/vectors/mosquitoes/Pages/aedes-aegypti.aspx |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2015年，[[白纹伊蚊|白纹伊蚊]]存在于美洲的热带、亚热带和温带地区，远至北美[[五大湖|五大湖]]。从国际上看，白纹伊蚊在部分热带和亚热带地区与埃及伊蚊共生<ref name="The global distribution of the arbovirus vectors" />。

埃及伊蚊一般在清晨和中午时分出动，其突出特征是它腿上的白色条纹<ref name="WHO Zika virus fact sheet">{{cite web |url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/zika/en/ |title=Zika virus fact sheet |publisher=World Health Organization |date=February 2016 |accessdate=2016-02-15 |archive-date=2016-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809235807/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/zika/en/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。传播寨卡病毒的蚊子品种（埃及伊蚊，主要是白纹伊蚊）也可以传播登革热、[[基孔肯雅热|基孔肯雅热]]和[[黄热病|黄热病]]<ref name="CDC Help Control Mosquitoes">{{cite web |url=http://www.cdc.gov/zika/pdfs/control_mosquitoes_chikv_denv_zika.pdf |title=Help Control Mosquitoes that Spread Dengue, Chikungunya, and Zika Viruses |publisher=Centers for Disease Control |work=Fact Sheets |date=August 2015 |accessdate=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017101354/https://www.cdc.gov/zika/pdfs/control_mosquitoes_chikv_denv_zika.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

本次疫情，阿根廷、加拿大、智利、法国、意大利、新西兰、秘鲁、葡萄牙和美国九国有寨卡性传播记录<ref name="CanadaSexTrans">{{cite news |url=http://outbreaknewstoday.com/canada-reports-1st-sexually-transmitted-zika-case-9th-country-to-report-person-to-person-transmission-88047/ |title=Canada reports 1st sexually transmitted Zika case, 9th country to report person-to-person transmission |work=Outbreak News Today |date=2016-04-26 |accessdate=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2016-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427124042/http://outbreaknewstoday.com/canada-reports-1st-sexually-transmitted-zika-case-9th-country-to-report-person-to-person-transmission-88047/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

孕妇可将寨卡传播给胎儿（{{le|垂直传播感染|Vertically transmitted infection|垂直传播}}），引发感染病毒的妇女产下有小头畸形及其他严重脑部异常的婴儿<ref name=RasmussenJamieson2016 /><ref name="WHO SitRep Apr 7, 2016"/>。

成人感染寨卡会出现[[格林－巴利综合征|格林－巴利综合征]]<ref name="WHO SitRep Apr 7, 2016"/>。

== 诊断 ==
{{main|茲卡熱}}
[[File:Microcephaly-comparison-500px.jpg|thumb]]。]]

症状类似于登革热或引发基孔肯雅热的{{le|甲病毒|Flavivirus}}<ref name="Musso14">{{cite journal |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1198743X1465391X |title=Rapid spread of emerging Zika virus in the Pacific area |last=Musso |first=D. |last2=Nilles |first2=E.J. |last3=Cao-Lormeau |first3=V.-M. |journal=Clinical Microbiology and Infection |year=2014 |volume=20 |issue=10 |pages=O595–6 |doi=10.1111/1469-0691.12707 |pmid=24909208 |access-date=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2018-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619140403/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1198743X1465391X |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但形式上较为轻微，一般持续两到七天<ref name="The emergence of zika virus" />。据估计80%的病例[[无症状|无症状]]<ref name="Interim Guidelines for Prevention of Sexual Transmission"/>。症状性患者的主要临床症状为低烧、[[结膜炎|结膜炎]]、短暂性关节疼痛（主要是手部和脚部的较小关节）及一般从脸部开始后扩散到全身的{{le|斑丘疹|maculopapular rash}}<ref name=Musso14 />。

由于与类似区域特有的其他蛛网膜病毒重叠，仅依靠临床体征和症状很难诊断寨卡病毒感染<ref name="Yet Another Arbovirus Threat">{{cite journal |url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMp1600297 |title=Zika Virus in the Americas – Yet Another Arbovirus Threat |date=2016-02-18 |last=Fauci |first=Anthony S. |last2=Morens |first2=David M. |journal=New England Journal of Medicine |volume=374 |issue=7 |pages=601–604 |doi=10.1056/NEJMp1600297 |pmid=26761185 |access-date=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2016-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316164910/http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMp1600297 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。目前能用的测试寨卡抗体的办法是与登革热抗体交叉反应。登革热[[免疫球蛋白M|IgM]]阳性结果或寨卡[[酶联免疫吸附试验|ELISA]]只能被认为是最近感染黄病毒的指示。减毒中和试验（PRINT）更具体<ref name="CDC Revised diagnostic testing for Zika">{{cite web |url=http://www.cdc.gov/zika/pdfs/denvchikvzikv-testing-algorithm.pdf |title=Revised diagnostic testing for Zika, chikungunya, and dengue viruses in US Public Health Laboratories |publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention |work=Division of Vector-Borne Diseases |date=2016-02-07 |accessdate=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2016-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320205410/http://www.cdc.gov/zika/pdfs/denvchikvzikv-testing-algorithm.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。使用[[逆转录聚合酶链式反应|RT-PCR]]可从急性病患者身上检测寨卡病毒<ref name="The emergence of zika virus" />。

RT-PCR血清和组织样本测试可用于检测寨卡病毒存在。然而，RT-PCR血清测试只有病毒通常在发病第一周中仍留在血液中才有用。过了这个时期，应用其他办法推断病毒
是否仍存在体内。IgM抗体测试有效时间更长，这些抗体在发病四天后才出现，可高达12个星期。然而，建议在测试IgM抗体后再进行PRINT测试，有助于消除其他黄病毒引发的假阳性。PRINT测试用于寻找病毒特异性中和抗体。然而，对于已经接种疫苗或此前曾接触其他黄病毒的个人而言，该试验检测寨卡病毒仍可能产生假阳性结果<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Karwowski|first1=Mateusz P.|last2=Nelson|first2=Jennifer M.|last3=Staples|first3=J. Erin|last4=Fischer|first4=Marc|last5=Fleming-Dutra|first5=Katherine E.|last6=Villanueva|first6=Julie|last7=Powers|first7=Ann M.|last8=Mead|first8=Paul|last9=Honein,|first9=Margaret A.|last10=Moore|first10=Cynthia A.|last11=Rasmussen|first11=Sonja A.|title=Zika Virus Disease: A CDC Update for Pediatric Health Care Providers|journal=Pediatrics|date=May 2016|volume=137|issue=5|pages=e20160621|doi=10.1542/peds.2016-0621|url=http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/content/137/5/e20160621?utm_source=highwire&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=Pediatrics_etoc|accessdate=2016-05-27|pmid=27009036|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919081512/https://pediatrics.aappublications.org/content/137/5/e20160621?utm_source=highwire&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=Pediatrics_etoc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 疫情防治 ==
=== 美洲 ===
哥伦比亚、厄瓜多尔、塞尔瓦多和牙买加等多国建议孕妇延迟分娩，直到风险被更加了解<ref name="Zika virus triggers pregnancy delay calls"/><ref name="Pregnant Irish women warned" />。巴西里约热内卢政府公布计划，严防寨卡病毒在[[2016年夏季奥运会|2016年夏季奥运会]]期间在里约传播<ref name="BBC-2016-01-24a">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-35394297 |title=Zika: Olympics plans announced by Rio authorities |work=BBC News |date=2016-01-24 |accessdate=2017-05-24 |archive-date=2020-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219235156/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-35394297 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年[[登革热|登革热]]疫情期间，{{le|秘鲁卫生部|Ministry of Health (Peru)}}布下20000多部[[诱蚊产卵器|诱蚊产卵器]]。秘鲁热带地区也采用同种诱蚊产卵器监测寨卡疫情爆发可能性<ref name="Northern Peru braces">{{cite news |last=Post |first=Colin |url=http://perureports.com/2016/01/25/northern-peru-braces-for-mosquito-borne-zika-virus/ |title=Northern Peru braces for mosquito-borne Zika virus |work=Peru Reports |date=2016-01-25 |accessdate=2017-05-24 |archive-date=2016-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128231352/http://perureports.com/2016/01/25/northern-peru-braces-for-mosquito-borne-zika-virus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年1月15日，鉴于“寨卡与小头畸形症有关的证据不断增长”，[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]]发布[[旅游警示|旅游警示]]，建议孕妇推迟前往巴西及报告寨卡热的国家和地区，包括哥伦比亚、塞尔瓦多、[[法属圭亚那|法属圭亚那]]、[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]、[[海地|海地]]、[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]、[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]、[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]、[[巴拿马|巴拿马]]、[[巴拉圭|巴拉圭]]、[[苏里南|苏里南]]、[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]和[[波多黎各|波多黎各联邦]]<ref name="Medscape – CDC Issues Zika Travel Alert">{{cite news |last=Lowes |first=Robert |url=http://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/857389?nlid=97363_3901&src=wnl_newsalrt_160115_MSCPEDIT&uac=28013DZ&impID=957011&faf=1 |title=CDC Issues Zika Travel Alert |work=Medscape Medical News |date=2016-01-15 |accessdate=2017-05-24 |archive-date=2016-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126092814/http://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/857389?nlid=97363_3901&src=wnl_newsalrt_160115_MSCPEDIT&uac=28013DZ&impID=957011&faf=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1月20日，{{le|智利卫生部|Ministry of Health (Chile)}}发布健康告示<ref name="Recomendaciones por Dengue Zika Chikungunya">{{cite web |url=http://web.minsal.cl/virus-zika/ |title=Recomendaciones por Dengue Zika Chikungunya |publisher=Chile Ministry of Health |date=2016-01-20 |language=es |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315024332/http://web.minsal.cl/virus-zika/ |archivedate=2016-03-15 |accessdate=2017-05-24 }}</ref>。1月22日，名单新增八个受影响国家和地区，有[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]、玻利维亚、厄瓜多尔、[[瓜德罗普|瓜德罗普]]、[[聖馬丁島|圣马丁]]、[[圭亚那|圭亚那]]、[[佛得角|佛得角]]和[[萨摩亚|萨摩亚]]<ref name="CDC expands Zika travel advisory">{{cite news |last=Branswell |first=Helen |url=http://www.statnews.com/2016/01/22/zika-travel-advisory-expanded/ |title=CDC expands Zika travel advisory to include more countries |work=Stat News |date=2016-01-22 |accessdate=2017-05-24 |archive-date=2016-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124041115/http://www.statnews.com/2016/01/22/zika-travel-advisory-expanded/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2月1日，[[哥斯达黎加|哥斯达黎加]]和[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]加入名单，受影响国家和地区数目达到28个<ref name="costaricanicaragua1">{{cite news |last1=Mohney |first1=Gillian |title=Latest on Zika Virus: WHO's Recommendations, CDC Advisory Expanded to 28 Countries |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Health/latest-zika-virus-recommendations-cdc-advisory-expanded-28/story?id=36664447 |accessdate=2016-02-28 |work=[[ABC新聞|ABC News]] |date=2016-02-02 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303104923/http://abcnews.go.com/Health/latest-zika-virus-recommendations-cdc-advisory-expanded-28/story?id=36664447 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。组织额外发布指南，建议打算生孩子的妇女在出行前咨询医师<ref name="CDC Interim Guidelines for Pregnant Women">{{cite journal |url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/volumes/65/wr/mm6502e1.htm |title=Interim Guidelines for Pregnant Women During a Zika Virus Outbreak – United States, 2016 |date=2016-01-22 |last=Petersen |first=Emily E. |last2=Staples |first2=J. Erin |last3=Meaney-Delman |first3=Dana |last4=Fischer |first4=Marc |last5=Ellington |first5=Sascha R. |last6=Callaghan |first6=William M. |last7=Jamieson |first7=Denise J. |journal=Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report |volume=65 |issue=2 |pages=30–33 |doi=10.15585/mmwr.mm6502e1 |pmid=26796813 |display-authors=2 |access-date=2017-05-24 |archive-date=2019-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191227051348/https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/volumes/65/wr/mm6502e1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加拿大也发布了类似于的出游建议<ref name="BBC-2016-01-24a" /><ref name="Government of Canada-2016-02-03a">{{cite web |url=http://travel.gc.ca/travelling/health-safety/travel-health-notices/143?_ga=1.191165994.1052850922.1446055028 |title=Zika virus infection in the Americas |publisher=Government of Canada |date=2016-02-03 |accessdate=2017-05-24 |archive-date=2016-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216025340/http://travel.gc.ca/travelling/health-safety/travel-health-notices/143?_ga=1.191165994.1052850922.1446055028 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2月5日，美国一名没有未到过疫区的男子与受感染的伴侣性接触，经实验室确诊感染寨卡病毒，疾病预防控制中心随后发布临时指南，预防寨卡病毒性传播<ref name="Interim Guidelines for Prevention of Sexual Transmission"/>。指南建议伴侣怀孕的男子若居住于或前往寨卡病毒传播活跃地区，应避免性活动，或在性交时坚持并正确使用避孕套<ref name="Interim Guidelines for Prevention of Sexual Transmission"/>，同时指南亦建议未怀孕的女性和她们的伴侣采用类似的措施<ref name="Interim Guidelines for Prevention of Sexual Transmission"/>。

2月8日，疾病预防控制中心将响应级别提升到最高的一级。在14份可能由性传播的病毒报告正在调查后，中心随后于2月23日发表声明，鼓励人们遵守指南<ref name="cdc1"/><ref name="nyttavernise"/>。3月11日，巴拉圭报告了该国首个孕妇寨卡病例<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.abc.com.py/nacionales/primer-caso-de-zika-en-embarazada-1460904.html|title=Paraguay: primer caso de zika en embarazada|work=ABC.com|date=2016-03-11|accessdate=2017-05-24|archive-date=2016-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625081716/http://www.abc.com.py/nacionales/primer-caso-de-zika-en-embarazada-1460904.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月18日，中心警告感染寨卡的人士切勿怀孕，称性交期间男方可能会把病毒传播给女方，转而影响胎儿。警告建议男性受感染六个月后才尝试受孕<ref name="STAT25Mar2016">{{cite news | url=http://www.statnews.com/2016/03/25/zika-new-cdc-recommendations/ | title=Couples exposed to Zika virus are urged to delay pregnancy | work=Stat News | date=2016-03-25 | last=Branswell | first=Helen | accessdate=2017-05-24 | archive-date=2016-03-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328162231/http://www.statnews.com/2016/03/25/zika-new-cdc-recommendations/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

4月14日，哥伦比亚报告了首例由寨卡病毒引起的小儿小头畸形症病例<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/04/15/world/americas/colombia-reports-first-cases-of-microcephaly-linked-to-zika-virus.html|title=Colombia Reports First Cases of Microcephaly Linked to Zika Virus|work=New York Times|date=2016-04-15|author1=Casey, Nicholas|author2=Díaz, María Eugenia|accessdate=2017-05-24|archive-date=2016-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616212832/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/04/15/world/americas/colombia-reports-first-cases-of-microcephaly-linked-to-zika-virus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中心4月28日授权急救中心使用寨卡病毒RNA定质测试检测出现感染症状的病人血液内寨卡病毒。首个用于急救的寨卡病毒商业测试由[[美国食品药品监督管理局|美国食品药品监督管理局]]授权<ref>{{cite web|title=Zika Virus Response Updates from FDA|url=http://www.fda.gov/EmergencyPreparedness/Counterterrorism/MedicalCountermeasures/MCMIssues/ucm485199.htm#bydate|accessdate=2016-04-29|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422171620/https://www.fda.gov/EmergencyPreparedness/Counterterrorism/MedicalCountermeasures/MCMIssues/ucm485199.htm#bydate|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月6日，[[美国职业棒球大联盟|美国职业棒球大联盟]]宣布原计划月底在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]][[圣胡安_(波多黎各)|圣胡安]]举行的[[迈阿密马林鱼|迈阿密马林鱼]]对阵[[匹兹堡海盗|匹兹堡海盗]]的系列赛改在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[迈阿密|迈阿密]][[马林鱼棒球场|马林鱼棒球场]]举行，回应球员们对暴露寨卡病毒风险的担忧<ref>{{cite news|last1=Almasy|first1=Steve|title=MLB moves games from Puerto Rico due to Zika concerns|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/05/06/health/mlb-puerto-rico-zika/|accessdate=2016-06-01|work=CNN|date=2016-05-06|archive-date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507120211/http://www.cnn.com/2016/05/06/health/mlb-puerto-rico-zika/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到8月中旬，至少有37人在邻近迈阿密的社区接触到病毒，但官员估计加上轻微病症报告，确切的感染人数可能要多得多<ref>{{cite web|last1=Doucleff|first1=Michaeleen|title=How Big, Really, Is The Zika Outbreak In Florida?|url=http://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2016/08/22/490941346/how-big-really-is-the-zika-outbreak-in-florida|website=NPR|accessdate=2016-08-23|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004233908/https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2016/08/22/490941346/how-big-really-is-the-zika-outbreak-in-florida|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月份，前往多米尼加共和国的游客推动纽约政府积极测试寨卡病毒<ref>{{cite web|title=Travelers to Dominican Republic Lead New York City in Positive Zika Tests|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/30/nyregion/dominicans-lead-among-those-testing-positive-for-zika-in-new-york-city.html|work=New York Times|date=2016-06-29|author=Santora, Mark|accessdate=2017-05-24|archive-date=2016-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161124224016/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/30/nyregion/dominicans-lead-among-those-testing-positive-for-zika-in-new-york-city.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 亚洲 ===
寨卡病毒感染于2016年6月传播到东南亚，[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[泰国|泰国]]和{{tsl|en|越南||越南}}成为受灾最严重的地区<ref name="hundreds confirmed cases"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-37548723|title=Zika virus: The outbreak in Asia|publisher=BBC News|date=2016-10-11|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2019-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007235305/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-37548723|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新加坡计划投入携带[[沃尔巴克氏体|沃尔巴克氏体]]菌的蚊子大军抗击埃及伊蚊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.thenational.ae/world/southeast-asia/in-fight-against-zika-singapore-releases-more-mosquitoes|title=In fight against Zika, Singapore releases more mosquitoes|author=Tan, Joanna|publisher=The National (UAE)|date=2016-10-16|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20161020223638/http://www.thenational.ae/world/southeast-asia/in-fight-against-zika-singapore-releases-more-mosquitoes}}</ref>。[[东南亚国家联盟|东南亚国家联盟]]增加信息分享并联合研究病毒<ref>{{cite web|url=http://asean.org/asean-health-ministers-respond-to-zika-virus/|title=ASEAN Health Ministers respond to Zika virus|publisher=[[东南亚国家联盟|ASEAN]]|date=2016-09-20|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021140958/http://asean.org/asean-health-ministers-respond-to-zika-virus/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.todayonline.com/world/asia/asean-pledges-boost-data-sharing-zika|title=Asean pledges to boost data-sharing on Zika|work=Bangkok Post|publisher=Today Online|date=2016-09-24|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021081257/http://m.todayonline.com/world/asia/asean-pledges-boost-data-sharing-zika|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月30日，泰国证实两名婴儿出生时出现小头畸形<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/09/zika-virus-thai-babies-diagnosed-microcephaly-160930152653089.html|title=Zika virus: Thailand babies diagnosed with microcephaly|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=2016-10-01|accessdate=2016-11-01|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101102110/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/09/zika-virus-thai-babies-diagnosed-microcephaly-160930152653089.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。病例出现前，泰国允许受出生畸形影响的孕妇流产<ref>{{cite web|url=http://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/diagnostics/abortion-legal-in-thai-birth-defect-cases-linked-to-zika-officials-say/54714732|title=Abortion legal in Thai birth defect cases linked to Zika, officials say|author=Amy Sawitta Lefevre|work=Reuters|publisher=ETHealthworld|date=2016-10-06|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021074130/http://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/diagnostics/abortion-legal-in-thai-birth-defect-cases-linked-to-zika-officials-say/54714732|archive-date=2016-10-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。马来西亚在这一问题上仍然犹豫不决<ref>{{cite web|url=https://asiancorrespondent.com/2016/09/malaysia-govt-muslim-clerics-split-abortion-zika-cases/|title=Malaysia: Govt, Muslim clerics split over abortion in Zika cases|publisher=Asian Correspondent|date=2016-09-01|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021135343/https://asiancorrespondent.com/2016/09/malaysia-govt-muslim-clerics-split-abortion-zika-cases/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该国医生将决定权交给母亲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nst.com.my/news/2016/10/177315/let-mother-decide|title=Let the mother decide|author=Soorian, A.|publisher=New Straits Times|date=2016-10-01|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021073556/http://www.nst.com.my/news/2016/10/177315/let-mother-decide|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马来西亚害虫防治公司Rentokil设计出蚊子综合治理（{{lang|en|Integrated Mosquito Management}}）计划抑制埃及伊蚊传播<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.digitaljournal.com/pr/3096400|title=Rentokil Malaysia Battling Rising Dengue and Zika Cases with Integrated Mosquito Management Programme|publisher=Digital Journal|accessdate=2016-10-21}}</ref>。10月17日，越南卫生部鉴于当地目前的病例数，宣布大流行<ref name="endemic Vietnam">{{cite news |url=http://tuoitrenews.vn/society/37590/zika-disease-becomes-endemic-in-vietnam-health-official |title=Zika disease becomes endemic in Vietnam: health official |publisher=Tuổi Trẻ |date=2016-10-17 |accessdate=2017-05-25 |archive-date=2016-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018211536/http://tuoitrenews.vn/society/37590/zika-disease-becomes-endemic-in-vietnam-health-official |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月31日，越南证实一名婴儿出生时出现小头畸形<ref>{{cite web|url=http://vietnamnews.vn/society/345333/vn-confirms-first-zika-tied-birth-defect-case.html|title=VN confirms first Zika-tied birth defect case|work=Vietnam News Agency|publisher=Việt Nam News|date=2016-10-31|accessdate=2016-11-01|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101044332/http://vietnamnews.vn/society/345333/vn-confirms-first-zika-tied-birth-defect-case.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]本土寨卡感染病例数目上升后，该国卫生部宣布大流行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rappler.com/nation/148215-zika-virus-endemic-philippines|title=DOH: Zika virus endemic in PH|author=Jee Y. Geronimo|publisher=Rappler|date=2016-10-04|accessdate=2016-11-21|archive-date=2016-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161120091445/http://www.rappler.com/nation/148215-zika-virus-endemic-philippines|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月28日，该国在教会召开“菲律宾全国对抗寨卡”国家峰会，发布教牧指南联合抑制病毒传播，提高当地社区对于蚊媒传播疾病的意识<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.doh.gov.ph/node/7552|title=DOH continues campaign against Zika as 3 new confirmed cases emerge|publisher=Department of Health (Philippines)|accessdate=2016-11-01|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101041728/http://www.doh.gov.ph/node/7552|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://reliefweb.int/report/world/zika-virus-microcephaly-and-guillain-barr-syndrome-situation-report-27-october-2016|title=Zika virus, Microcephaly and Guillain-Barré syndrome Situation Report, 27 October 2016|publisher=ReliefWeb|date=2016-10-27|accessdate=2016-11-01|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101041651/http://reliefweb.int/report/world/zika-virus-microcephaly-and-guillain-barr-syndrome-situation-report-27-october-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.radiovaticana.va/news/2016/10/29/church_in_philippines_joins_fight_against_zika/1268660|title=Church in Philippines joins fight against Zika|publisher=Vatican Radio|date=2016-10-29|accessdate=2016-11-01|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101044002/http://en.radiovaticana.va/news/2016/10/29/church_in_philippines_joins_fight_against_zika/1268660|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[中華民國|台湾]]感染病例也出现增长，大部分病例据信是从他国输入的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cdc.gov.tw/english/info.aspx?treeid=BC2D4E89B154059B&nowtreeid=EE0A2987CFBA3222&tid=B457AF423C41CBDB|title=As CECC for Zika Virus confirms 13th imported Zika case, travelers returning from Zika-affected areas advised to take precautions against mosquito bites, follow "1+6 Principle" and seek immediate medical attention when symptoms develop|publisher=Centers for Disease Control (Taiwan)|date=2016-10-17|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2019-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203045255/https://www.cdc.gov.tw/english/info.aspx?treeid=BC2D4E89B154059B&nowtreeid=EE0A2987CFBA3222&tid=B457AF423C41CBDB|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月27日，[[缅甸|缅甸]]宣布首例输入病例，病人是外国孕妇<ref name="Myanmar"/>。

